Class TetrisGrid

  • java.lang.Object
    • TetrisGrid

  • public class TetrisGrid
extends java.lang.Object
    TetrisGrid.java This is the model class. TetrisGrid sets up the game play area. Sets the rules for movement and creates new Tetris pieces.
    Author:
    adelyn.yeoh CS201 - Tetris
